SUMMARY:Tryon Creek State Natural Area: Saturday Guided Nature Walks
DESCRIPTION:Category: Parks & Nature\nCost: Park FREE\; Parking $10/day res
 idents\, $12/day non-residents (since Oct 1\, 2025)\nNote: Free if arrivin
 g by foot\, bike\, or bus. Annual permits $60 resident/$75 non-resident.\n
 Info: One-hour guided hike with a park naturalist. Topics vary weekly - fu
 ngi\, wildlife\, seasonal themes. Ages 5+ (all ages welcome). No registrat
 ion - meet at Nature Center.\nAddress: 11321 S Terwilliger Blvd\, Portland
 \, OR 97219\nPhone: 503-636-9886\nWebsite: https://stateparks.oregon.gov/i
 ndex.cfm?do=park.profile&parkId=103
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 3.2//EN"><HTML><BODY><p><strong>Category:</strong> Parks &amp; Nature</p><p><strong>Cost:</strong> Park FREE; Parking $10/day residents, $12/day non-residents (since Oct 1, 2025)</p><p><em>Free if arriving by foot, bike, or bus. Annual permits $60 resident/$75 non-resident.</em></p><p>One-hour guided hike with a park naturalist. Topics vary weekly - fungi, wildlife, seasonal themes. Ages 5+ (all ages welcome). No registration - meet at Nature Center.</p><p><strong>Address:</strong> 11321 S Terwilliger Blvd, Portland, OR 97219</p><p><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:503-636-9886">503-636-9886</a></p><p><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://stateparks.oregon.gov/index.cfm?do=park.profile&parkId=103">https://stateparks.oregon.gov/index.cfm?do=park.profile&amp;parkId=103</a></p></BODY></HTML>
